rrency\nThis requires **System** level (real separate OS processes).\n\n**Behavior 5 — _migrations table created**: On a fresh database, the table doesn't exist. The code must create it before inserting migration metadata. A Unit test could mock table existence, but wouldn't verify the schema. A real database ensures the schema is correct. **Integration**."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13373,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13373},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8af9b6fe-06ab-45b9-a67b-a5e7eed87494","uuid":"2d871507-73a4-407e-a814-bf9ae4aaf97b"}
